<section class="sectionWrapper veridoc-global-sec">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="section-title text-start">
                    <h4>VERIDOC GLOBAL</h4>
                    <h2>SOLUTION</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <p>
                            VeriDoc Global has developed a solution that involves embedding a QR code on an item with
                            a unique digital hash inside the QR code. The hash holds a string of information that is
                            then placed on the blockchain network for security, verification and most important end
                            user validation. Using a QR code reading app, customers can scan the QR code on the item
                            once it has been delivered to them to verify the authenticity of items.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <p>
                            Throughout the shipping process, the QR code can be updated with information verifying
                            when and where the product has changed hands. Using any QR code reading app, scan the QR
                            code on the pharmaceuticals and the app will show you the true document produced by the
                            issuer. This allows you to compare and see if the pharmaceuticals is an original or a
                            fake.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/assets/img/Use-cases/phone-qr.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>



